00:00:00.256 --> 00:00:02.560
<b>Reaching for an item with your preferred hand</b>

00:00:02.816 --> 00:00:05.376
<b>is a common cause of stressful twisting and bending.</b>

00:00:05.888 --> 00:00:07.680
<b>A simple way to reduce the stress</b>

00:00:07.936 --> 00:00:08.960
<b>is to point your toe</b>

00:00:09.216 --> 00:00:11.004
<b>and reach with the same-side hand.</b>

00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:13.568
<b>Then, pass the item to your preferred hand.</b>

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:16.784
<b>This simple application of Point Your Toe and Go</b>

00:00:16.896 --> 00:00:18.744
<b>is called a center-line hand off.</b>

